                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to <persName
                            type="to">Cardinal Rampolla</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-07-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 20, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President desires me to express his profound sense of loss which the
                    Christian world has sustained in the death of His Holiness Leo XIII. By his
                    lofty character, his great learning, and his comprehensive charity, he adorned
                    his exalted station and made his reign one of the most illustrious as it has
                    been one of the longest in the history of the Catholic Church.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">John Hay.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
